Package: homelab-siem-scanner
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, curl, jq, openssl, apt-transport-https, gnupg2
Suggests: ufw, nmap, clamav, wireguard-tools
Description: Integrated Home Lab SIEM and Security Scanner Orchestrator
 This package automates the secure local deployment, network isolation,
 and baseline hardening rules for a unified Wazuh SIEM ecosystem. It 
 automatically provisions host firewall rules (UFW), initializes threat
 detection tools (ClamAV, Nmap), and bootstraps the centralized central
 monitoring manager, indexing nodes, and visual dashboard interfaces.
